<strong>第三個僕人因著怠惰，而將主人給他的一千銀子埋在地底下。</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n　　主人回來了，前兩個僕人都獲得主人稱讚與獎賞。主人氣憤的稱第三僕人為「又惡又懶的僕人」，把他丟在外面的黑暗裡，這是他應得的結果。 <br />\n<br />\n使乜驚 第三僕人個老豆係 劉鑾雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"我諗起另一個故事<br />\n<br />\n晉惠帝執政時期曾發生饑荒，許多百姓活活餓死。但從未走出過皇宮的晉惠帝天天錦衣玉食，完全不懂得民間的疾苦。所以當他聽說百姓因為沒有米飯吃而餓死了，覺得大惑不解。他反問大臣：既然他們沒有米飯充饑，為何不吃用肉煮的粥呢？&nbsp;"},{"pid":"a4436fcc0ecd12a1a73d9265edb142af959e138e","tid":799499,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66e3cdfc4411ca688b5941a2670b19ffb8287ab","tid":799499,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cefe5fe653e8877b044b5bf0b11e7e45fcb9eb31","tid":799499,"uid":9053,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"十萬連甘比個手袋都買唔起啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"佢老豆玩西女人都唔止喇"},{"pid":"e00c67722aa79bce32544317ef5620be13c19c8d","tid":799499,"uid":1928,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"佢老豆見個仔十歲比左十皮想試下佢<br />\n點知個仔咁撚弱智<br />\n拎左十皮日日玩數銀紙<br />\n從此以後當佢廢柴咁養大就算<br />\n搞成佢今日咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7ff307f3d11836cd0eac38dc0d86a12d15310b","tid":799499,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:45:04.000Z","msg":"仲有幾千億，我仲有幾千億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我未夠26，老豆佢都出張黑卡畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10887d9a00fc589ffc7f39533438c0709310fe7b","tid":799499,"uid":63909,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e00c67722aa79bce32544317ef5620be13c19c8d","tid":799499,"uid":1928,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T01:43:24.000Z","ms